race.description: Ladbrokes Launceston Cup Packages On Sale (C6)
race.comment: THOROS OF MYR (2) may cap off a good day for the Trinder yard. He's a leader who was caught late here last time over 1200m in stronger grade. He won a 72 prior over this distance, and that stacks right up. Keeps the in-form hoop and he can bounce back in a suitable race. GEMS EAGLE (5) resumes seeking the hat-trick off longer sprints. He's trialled well and looks ready to go. Has the figures to threaten. FLYING BILLIE (1) resumes and can make the finish if presented forward. 2x winning rider Pires is reunited. May find the 1100m a touch sharp, but he can't be taken lightly regardless. POPILITA (6) will strip fitter and can fill a slot at best.
